headline: Should Investors Rethink Cboe Stock After Recent 22% Gain in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether now is the right time to buy, sell, or hold Cboe Global Markets, you are not alone. The stock has a history of surprising both skeptics and fans, offering strong returns that would make any long-term investor pause for a second look. Over the last five years, Cboe’s share price has risen by a staggering 197.2%, easily outpacing the broader market and drawing attention from investors searching for growth.
